comment_data.body: It looks like your `pubspec.yaml` file is bad. Try running `flutter pub get` from a terminal. You may need to delete the `pubspec.yaml` file first. Let us know if that helps.
Thanks~,I didn't do anything, just restart ide. This error report was never received again.
